          <p>Our competition awards one winner with "charitable superpowers" - which we define as: The ability to give away money every year, to any cause, person or ogranization where it creates a positive impact regardless of your personal financial status." One winner will have the ability to give away $300 every year for the rest of their lives.</p>
        </details>
      </li>
